{"tid":1548513,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想去機場既同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-07T04:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T05:04:58.000Z","uid":285910,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2438de9624d1d34d592648a844650615b9ac80","tid":1548513,"uid":285910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"我等左呢一日好耐！<br />\n<br />\n事關今日機場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Novotel</span></span> 既Essence 餐廳終於有<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">荔枝番石榴週末「夏」午茶自助餐</span></span></strong>！！<br />\n<br />\n平時無架，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">週末限定</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n咁多嘢食都只係$158，真係專登搭程車去都抵返<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔係唔去啊？？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/07/123623_5b0686f41107727aa5f92d98db5c9548.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F123623_5b0686f41107727aa5f92d98db5c9548.png&h=5a6e8a0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00276c2b974833ed3cee36191b342f1b40df111d","tid":1548513,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"荔枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485ad604326f66aeb7e0ff7a27775f4088e1becc","tid":1548513,"uid":285910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00276c2b974833ed3cee36191b342f1b40df111d","tid":1548513,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"荔枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"有無人約埋一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec778a1f323f0eddd5f9e87b2b6906f558a02a51","tid":1548513,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b97b48eeb64822f872cb07a4c2937934deaaec13","tid":1548513,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔敢自己去 搵人陪我ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc7d8695390e5f4784a38110f303c13f3a761cf","tid":1548513,"uid":8007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"credit to 你把我灌腸巴打<br />\n太有用幫佢copy and paste<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴士撚here<br />\n雖然我係P牌仔，<br />\n但利申我係巴士公司做左幾年駐守機場<br />\n首先入柏麗灣係無用既，最多都係塞到馬灣<br />\n因為柏麗灣巴士只經青馬大橋但唔經收費站<br />\n如果想塞青馬收費站<br />\n<br />\n揸車組：瘋狂揸車出入青馬比金牛佢找錢，<br />\n或者過收費站個陣狂玩野e.g. 係咁摷錢、喪問野、全數比晒毫子 etc.<br />\n<br />\n搭車組：青馬收費站有條循環線入迪士尼叫 R8<br />\n呢條線係 迪士尼開，經迪欣湖，之後去青馬收費站(北行)，再過橋U turn返青馬收費站(南行)，然後又返迪欣湖同迪士尼，全程唔落車都係收$7<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想搭呢條R8都無問題，<br />\n可以搭任何一架E線/A線巴士，<br />\n去到青馬收費站(南行)落車，<br />\n再用行人隧道過對面青馬收費站(北行)搭返出市區<br />\n提提各位：城巴A線用八達通比錢，即日回程個程車係有半價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而E線最平果3條線都係 $10.8 分別係<br />\nE31 荃灣愉景新城 &lt;&gt; 逸東邨<br />\nE32 葵芳南 &lt;&gt; 機場博覽館<br />\nE32A 葵芳南 &lt;&gt; 東涌碼頭 (經:荃灣)<br />\n<br />\n而勇武組就自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過如果勇武rb塞青馬收費站似乎唔太可行<br />\n因為狗可以即時去果個位清場<br />\n可能手足未塞晒個陣警畜已經出左黎<br />\n同埋如果有手足要走先，<br />\n封左路就需要行返欣澳站搭鐵走<br />\n或者欣澳站搭去愉景灣轉船走<br />\n<br />\n仲有澄清返其實901個日大部份人都係搭巴士入去機場<br />\n因為黨鐵機場一出根本就入唔到T1甚至出唔到機場巴士總站<br />\n全靠勇武衝爆左機鐵站手足先入到去<br />\n總之屯門至赤鱲角隧道未通車之前，<br />\n青馬收費站就係機場既春袋，<br />\n2015年有船hi到青馬大橋搞到封橋，<br />\n成個大嶼山同機場即變荒島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41ad6af79eb3537aed1834c9f76614e738f4d27","tid":1548513,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"novotel 喺東涌喎師兄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過入東涌已經夠做"},{"pid":"2eabce02cb7778344f492bdba4e3277e3a86bb12","tid":1548513,"uid":241106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"推 又幾好wor"},{"pid":"70112b5a9990713f3ebd2e97a0225ac53db65d3c","tid":1548513,"uid":285910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d41ad6af79eb3537aed1834c9f76614e738f4d27","tid":1548513,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"novotel 喺東涌喎師兄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過入東涌已經夠做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"酒店話只需要5分鐘就有專車送客去機場，真係細心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5db6c70113f8ee36f3a664863ec96c068acb78","tid":1548513,"uid":285910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b97b48eeb64822f872cb07a4c2937934deaaec13","tid":1548513,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔敢自己去 搵人陪我ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"約定你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9f8b0dcf0b7cc5bfe8e1888782f26e43b01761","tid":1548513,"uid":285910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2eabce02cb7778344f492bdba4e3277e3a86bb12","tid":1548513,"uid":241106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"推 又幾好wor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:04:58.000Z","msg":"又有荔枝又有番石榴你重想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}